6 Gene modules

6.1 Idenfity gene modules

The results above indicates that there are 18 gene modules, labeled 1 through 1 in order of descending size. The largest module has 609 genes, and the smallest module has 34 genes. The label 0 is reserved for genes outside of all modules.
